<br>
• You hit with each weapon every time you hit an enemy <br>
• You automatically do half damage with each weapon<br>
• You do 20% more damage per round (10% per weapon) <br>
• Half your skill level is added as a % bonus<br>
• The attack delay is determined by an average of the two weapons<br>
<br>
so the equation for leftaxe should be<br>
<br>
60%+(SKILL * .5) <br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
and not 60%+(Skill * .25)<br>
<br>
<br>
